songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Y'all niggas don't
Y'all niggas don't want to see a nigga really do some throwed shit like
Do that shit raw no... no ski mask

[Chorus]
Ayy, slide wit' no ski, I did it raw
Like my sushi fried, this time I need it raw
Ayy, hit her with no condom, beat it raw
Niggas tried to catch me lackin' at the mall
Fuck your bitch, I break her back, I beat her jaw (Yeah, yeah)
If you seen, better no say what you saw (Yeah, yeah)
King Slime told me move just like the mob
I got real killers behind me and they armed

[Verse 1]
I got them shooters behind me and they yawnin'
Let's be honest, y'all niggas don't want to see me wit' no conscience
Cut all that fake shit, pretendin' and that flodgin'
Catch a nigga on the set, if he lackin', I'ma off him
Woah, woah, oh no
Catch a nigga down bad, watch him die slow
I'm on house arrest, I can't even tote the pole
Bitch what's up? I ain't goin' out like a ho
Ayy, struck nigga quick, I don't even bowl
Should work at a laundromat, how y'all niggas fold (Ayy)
Young ass nigga, but I'm ten toes
I ain't tryna hide my pain, I'ma let it show

[Chorus]
Ayy, slide wit' no ski, I did it raw
Like my sushi fried, this time I need it raw
Ayy, hit her with no condom, beat it raw
Niggas tried to catch me lackin' at the mall
Fuck your bitch, I break her back, I beat her jaw (Yeah, yeah)
If you seen, better no say what you saw (Yeah, yeah)
King Slime told me move just like the mob
I got real killers behind me and they armed

[Outro]
Aight, let me get it
songs.title: Raw
